data.description: Come and see this newly painted 2 story corner lot home. Large primary BR with cathedral ceiling, study room, 4 BR with ceiling light fixtures and large walk-in closets, 2 full BA with 2 separate vanities and 1/2 BA. Cathedral ceiling at foyer, granite countertops, electric stove, family room with fireplace, water softener throughout the house convey "as is". Excellent location closest to Cedar Rd.
